'''吉姆·弗莱厄蒂'''（{{lang-en|James Michael Jim Flaherty}}，{{bd|1949年|12月30日|2014年|4月10日|catIdx=Flaherty}}），是一名加拿大政治家，他在2006年2月6日至2014年3月18日但是加拿大联邦财政部长。他在2013年至2014年為加拿大代總理，即總理不方便出席或死亡時，代表總理議政或繼任為代總理。

早年毕业于[[普林斯顿大学|普林斯顿大学]]<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/careers/careers-leadership/jim-flaherty-time-off-the-hustings-tucking-into-soup/article576562/?page=all|accessdate=2014-03-25|title=Jim Flaherty: Time off the hustings, tucking into soup|publisher=[[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]]|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221254/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/careers/careers-leadership/jim-flaherty-time-off-the-hustings-tucking-into-soup/article576562/?page=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2006年，担任加拿大联邦财政部长。

2013年5月21日，他经营2013年财政计划，包括重建加拿大基础设施计划<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.journalofcommerce.com/article/id54666/profenvironmental|accessdate=2014-03-25|title=Building Canada Plan maps infrastructure spending|publisher=Journal of Commerce|archive-date=2013-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130426233847/http://www.journalofcommerce.com/article/id54666/profenvironmental|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，包括提供530亿元投资支持地方经济基础设施建造<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.thewesternstar.com/News/Local/2013-03-22/article-3205324/Greeley-pleased-to-see-new-Building-Canada-plan-in-federal-budget/1|accessdate=2014-03-25|title=Greeley pleased to see new Building Canada plan in federal budget|publisher=[[The_Western_Star_(Corner_Brook)|The Western Star]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130802192839/http://www.thewesternstar.com/News/Local/2013-03-22/article-3205324/Greeley-pleased-to-see-new-Building-Canada-plan-in-federal-budget/1|archivedate=2013-08-02}}</ref>。2014年3月18日，他离任并回到地方事务<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/read-jim-flahertys-statement-on-resigning-as-finance-minister/article17551462/#dashboard/follows/|accessdate=2014-03-25|title=Read Jim Flaherty's statement on resigning as finance minister|publisher=[[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]]|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306042547/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/read-jim-flahertys-statement-on-resigning-as-finance-minister/article17551462/#dashboard/follows/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年4月10日，他因病去世，享年64岁<ref>{{cite news|title=Former finance minister Jim Flaherty is dead at 64|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/flaherty/article17919447/|accessdate=April 10, 2014|newspaper=The Globe and Mail|date=April 10, 2014|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205123555/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/flaherty/article17919447/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

